{"tid":888182,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓價回調】海富苑呎價跌穿9000元 較數日前同類成交平近百萬","createTime":"2018-11-03T13:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T05:35:59.000Z","uid":83582,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29880f9f05f562fe8638cc8812f8719fc9a69d4c","tid":888182,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"16:00 2018/11/03<br />\n<br />\n【樓價回調】海富苑呎價跌穿9000元 較數日前同類成交平近百萬<br />\n代理：內籠殘裝拖低造價<br />\n<br />\n熱門屋苑之一的大角咀海富苑再錄回調成交，樓價與日前同類成交相差近百萬，未補價呎價跌穿9000元水平。<br />\n<br />\n世紀21家天下物業富榮花園分行經理黎振傑指出，屋苑海寧閣中低層12室，實用面積546平方呎，剛以未補價468萬元易手，樓價跌穿「5球」，呎價8,571元，呎價跌穿9000元水平。<br />\n<br />\n首先，日前錄得1宗白居二入市個案，為同座中層單位，造價565萬元，樓價相隔約5層，是次成交價足足低97萬或17.2%。另去年2月同座中低層3室，造價451萬及呎價8,260元。<br />\n<br />\n其次，屋苑對上一宗呎價8000餘元的成交，已經要追溯至去年5月。對比同類單位中高層戶今年高位呎價要10,961元，高位回落達21.8%。<br />\n<br />\n為何是次成交價可以相差近百萬？黎振傑解釋，是次成交單位內籠殘裝，拖低造價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2200566/%E3%80%90%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF%E3%80%91%E6%B5%B7%E5%AF%8C%E8%8B%91%E5%91%8E%E5%83%B9%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF9000%E5%85%83%20%E8%BC%83%E6%95%B8%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%A1%9E%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B3%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC?mtc=60007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2200566%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%258B%2591%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%25A9%25BF9000%25E5%2585%2583%2520%25E8%25BC%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E9%25A1%259E%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D60007&d=pFvIwGAAXNdDs4Zg8llnlU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=dc6dd804\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2200566/%E3%80%90%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%9E%E8%AA%BF%E3%80%91%E6%B5%B7%E5%AF%8C%E8%8B%91%E5%91%8E%E5%83%B9%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF9000%E5%85%83%20%E8%BC%83%E6%95%B8%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%A1%9E%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B3%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC?mtc=60007</a>"},{"pid":"99d5f79485ef49d1c58db2c4958eac86136b3de4","tid":888182,"uid":28245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"8500 一尺住奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da2261f334a06d5cbd032e19830be6cc73d0a25","tid":888182,"uid":122377,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"個個買完 都重新裝修架啦 <br />\n又唔係半新樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b504d1b9ee5d7da7ecd5b1edfedc92b77b3c6d6","tid":888182,"uid":39706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"唔知嗰位白居二睇到有咩感想?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b119c201fa56e29bde54f33379cc3dcd9a4bfac","tid":888182,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"不過海富唯一唔好係同公屋無異<br />\n得佢一座係居 但用料外觀都同公屋一樣"},{"pid":"a67bb62f48921db07769bbe4c608cd44b822c861","tid":888182,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91f063635aa97b1b5919684cb4ffa918d31d9749","tid":888182,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"再跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34042b62318901f1b157392d559d26c20ac4627a","tid":888182,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"呢個真係抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1436bb8f1a7da3791f16154908be41b2ba45e008","tid":888182,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"篇文寫到1999 咁<br />\n<br />\n跌左幾多？"},{"pid":"405c2ab6159af6c3cb977a627275a0366705d4fc","tid":888182